_sText:
Map I spent a while making for some german shmuck, slightly over a minute in length and has a nice bonus. I originally was going to make this a one shot then realised it worked better with checkpoints, so a couple of checkpoints are shit if you fail in an awkward position, but I guess it doesn't matter much since most people will try to oneshot it anyway.



Big Thanks to those who tested and thanks to Nallie for the bonus.
